<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Fitness Journey - Humzah Imam</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css"> <!-- Link to external CSS file in the public folder -->
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Include the header partial for navigation -->
    <% include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Fitness Journey Section -->
    <main>
        <section class="about-section">
            <h1>My Fitness Journey</h1>
            <p>Welcome to my fitness journey! Here, you will find a collection of videos showcasing my transformation, workouts, and motivational content. Fitness is not just a hobby for me—it's a lifestyle that I’m continuously dedicated to.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Profile Photo (Kept Same) -->
        <section class="media-section" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <div class="profile-photo">
                <img src="/images/HumzahPhoto1.jpg" alt="Humzah Imam" width="400px">
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Fitness Videos Section (All Videos Same Size) -->
        <section class="media-section" style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 20px;">
            <div class="fitness-videos">
                <video width="400px" height="500px" controls>
                    <source src="/videos/TransformationVideo.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                    Your browser does not support the video tag.
                </video>

                <video width="400px" height="500px" controls>
                    <source src="/videos/MotivationalFitnessVideo1.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                    Your browser does not support the video tag.
                </video>

                <video width="400px" height="500px" controls>
                    <source src="/videos/MotivationalFitnessVideo2.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                    Your browser does not support the video tag.
                </video>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Include the footer partial -->
    <% include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
